00:00:04.050 --> 00:00:07.009
The Graduation that Never Was

00:00:07.009 --> 00:00:13.120
Thomas Bartlett, living in Sugar Land Texas
was a privileged and pompous teenager who

00:00:13.120 --> 00:00:17.860
was showered in luxury and love by his affluent
parents.

00:00:17.860 --> 00:00:23.619
He attended Clements High school but was expelled
after committing a series of burglaries.

00:00:23.619 --> 00:00:29.019
As part of the expulsion process he was evaluated
by a mental health professional who stated

00:00:29.019 --> 00:00:34.980
Thomas was suffering from “ clinical symptoms
of delusional paranoid disorder”.

00:00:34.980 --> 00:00:41.050
Ignoring the clinicians diagnosis, Thomas’s
parents spared no expense in giving him a

00:00:41.050 --> 00:00:43.360
lifestyle of opulence.

00:00:43.360 --> 00:00:48.500
Staunch supporters of their son, the Whitakers
purchased Thomas a lakeside home in Texas

00:00:48.500 --> 00:00:52.609
to live rent free so he could attend the college
nearby.

00:00:52.609 --> 00:00:58.019
Gifting him multiple luxury vehicles and paying
the steep university tuition, the Whitakers

00:00:58.019 --> 00:01:03.839
were not immune to Thomas’s charm and perchance
for crafting tales of success.

00:01:03.839 --> 00:01:09.860
Thomas told them he was doing extremely well
in college and would be graduating on time.

00:01:09.860 --> 00:01:15.750
On the day of his “graduation” they presented
him with a brand new $4000 Rolex watch as

00:01:15.750 --> 00:01:17.690
a “graduation present.”

00:01:17.690 --> 00:01:18.840
The catch?

00:01:18.840 --> 00:01:20.550
He never graduated.

00:01:20.550 --> 00:01:23.300
He was never even enrolled at the college.

00:01:23.300 --> 00:01:29.020
And hours after receiving this luxury Rolex
he would come to kill the very people who

00:01:29.020 --> 00:01:32.790
gifted to him the world.

00:01:32.790 --> 00:01:38.970
On December 10, 2003 Thomas falsely boasted
to his parents that he just finished his final

00:01:38.970 --> 00:01:42.290
exams and was looking forward to graduating.

00:01:42.290 --> 00:01:48.330
To celebrate they drove to the Pappadeaux
restaurant with Thomas and enjoyed what, unbeknownst

00:01:48.330 --> 00:01:50.460
to them, would be their last meal.

00:01:50.460 --> 00:01:55.820
What the Whitakers didn’t know was that
her son had been living a lie.

00:01:55.820 --> 00:01:57.820
He was not about to graduate college.

00:01:57.820 --> 00:02:00.040
He wasn’t even enrolled in college.

00:02:00.040 --> 00:02:04.630
And his lies were so deeply embedded into
his world that he couldn’t bear the idea

00:02:04.630 --> 00:02:07.090
of his parents finding out the truth.

00:02:07.090 --> 00:02:12.030
So he sought out the help of Christopher Brashear
and Steven Champagne to make sure that the

00:02:12.030 --> 00:02:14.350
truth would never come out.

00:02:14.350 --> 00:02:18.920
While the Whitakers were enjoying a family
meal, accomplice Christopher Brashear let

00:02:18.920 --> 00:02:24.560
himself in to the Whitaker family home and,
following Thomas’s instructions, helped

00:02:24.560 --> 00:02:29.440
himself to the husband’s gun and bullets
from a safe box in his bedroom.

00:02:29.440 --> 00:02:35.490
He ransacked the house to make it appear as
if a burglary had taken place, and then lay

00:02:35.490 --> 00:02:39.670
in wait for the fated family to return home.

00:02:39.670 --> 00:02:45.450
Meanwhile Steven Champagne tailed the family
home where he waited as a getaway car.

00:02:45.450 --> 00:02:49.820
When the family arrived, Thomas said that
he had to grab his cell phone from his parked

00:02:49.820 --> 00:02:54.120
car and separated momentarily from the rest
of the family.

00:02:54.120 --> 00:03:00.040
The family entered the house, with the younger
brother Kevin, 19, leading the way.

00:03:00.040 --> 00:03:05.850
When Kevin initially saw the masked intruder
he thought it was a prank being told off by

00:03:05.850 --> 00:03:08.709
one of Thomases friends in honor of his graduation.

00:03:08.709 --> 00:03:15.290
But when he was shot once in the chest and
collapsed to the floor his mother, Patricia

00:03:15.290 --> 00:03:20.990
screamed out “Oh God No” and all pretenses
of a light hearted prank flew out the window.

00:03:20.990 --> 00:03:27.500
Can’t, Patricia‘s husband of 26 years
ran inside and was subsequently shot in the

00:03:27.500 --> 00:03:28.500
shoulder.

00:03:28.500 --> 00:03:33.190
Thomas, returning from his car, then ran into
the house and pretended to struggle with the

00:03:33.190 --> 00:03:38.870
gunman, getting shot himself in his left arm
as a way to stage his innocence.

00:03:38.870 --> 00:03:43.160
The gunman then ran out the back door and
hopped over the fence and jumped into the

00:03:43.160 --> 00:03:44.620
getaway car.

00:03:44.620 --> 00:03:49.990
Kevin, the little brother, died almost instantly
and his mother, Patricia, died while being

00:03:49.990 --> 00:03:52.490
airlifted to the nearby hospital.

00:03:52.490 --> 00:03:58.319
The father, Kent, was also airlifted to the
hospital and survive the murder attempt.

00:03:58.319 --> 00:04:04.630
Thomas, an an attempt to divert suspicion,
initially told officers that their attacker

00:04:04.630 --> 00:04:05.630
was African-American.

00:04:05.630 --> 00:04:13.010
Kent, Thomases father, initially vowed to
forgive whomever murdered his family but his

00:04:13.010 --> 00:04:18.190
face was shaken when it was revealed that
his precious son, who had been living and

00:04:18.190 --> 00:04:22.689
recovering with Kent before fleeing to Mexico
upon hearing that he was going to soon be

00:04:22.689 --> 00:04:26.320
arrested, was actually the murderer.

00:04:26.320 --> 00:04:32.810
Thomas hid in Mexico under the assumed name
of Rudy Rios for almost a year until, in September

00:04:32.810 --> 00:04:39.960
of 2005, Mexican authorities delivered him
back to the US to face trial.

00:04:39.960 --> 00:04:44.659
During the trial Christopher Breshear claimed
Thomas promised a cut of the million dollar

00:04:44.659 --> 00:04:51.240
insurance policy taken out on his parents,
but it was revealed no such policy existed.

00:04:51.240 --> 00:04:58.509
In actuality, Thomas committed murders out
of shame and cowardice- he was terrified of

00:04:58.509 --> 00:05:00.560
the truth coming out.

00:05:00.560 --> 00:05:05.900
Nevertheless Kent Whitaker stuck by his son
side and believed him when he blamed his mental

00:05:05.900 --> 00:05:07.979
illness for the evil deeds.

00:05:07.979 --> 00:05:13.639
Thomas, ever the master manipulator, even
went so far as to claim that his death penalty

00:05:13.639 --> 00:05:18.939
conviction would further victimize his father
as he would lose his only remaining son.

00:05:18.939 --> 00:05:24.689
Shockingly, Kent, his father, stayed by his
side and testified repeatedly that he had

00:05:24.689 --> 00:05:26.139
forgiven his son.

00:05:26.139 --> 00:05:32.530
Originally Thomas’s execution date was set
for early 2018 but upon his fathers ferocious

00:05:32.530 --> 00:05:37.699
fighting his sentence was changed from “death”
to life in prison without the possibility

00:05:37.699 --> 00:05:39.509
of parole.

