00:05:41.169 --> 00:05:44.789
W.H.O is Jean Claude Romand (get it?

00:05:44.789 --> 00:05:46.550
World Health Organization- W.H.O?!)

00:05:46.550 --> 00:05:51.729
Born in Lons-le-Saunier, Jean Claude Romand
was not the studious type.

00:05:51.729 --> 00:05:57.060
After graduating high school he signed up
for college classes at the Lucee du Parc,

00:05:57.060 --> 00:06:03.190
but, unable to handle the grueling academics
he dropped out after only one semester.

00:06:03.190 --> 00:06:07.870
He reenrolled as a medical student but still
couldn’t handle the workload.

00:06:07.870 --> 00:06:13.400
His lies began when he told his family that
he had passed a second-year Final exam that

00:06:13.400 --> 00:06:16.900
would enable him to begin the process of becoming
a doctor.

00:06:16.900 --> 00:06:20.120
The problem was, he never took the exam.

00:06:20.120 --> 00:06:25.389
That lie would catapult into a full-blown
second life in which he was a successful doctor

00:06:25.389 --> 00:06:30.590
for the world health organization researching
the hardening and thickening of arteries and

00:06:30.590 --> 00:06:34.610
had very prestigious academic and political
connections.

00:06:34.610 --> 00:06:38.969
He kept this highly specific lie up for 18
years.

00:06:38.969 --> 00:06:44.860
In all actuality Romand would spend his days
at the world health organization, however

00:06:44.860 --> 00:06:49.180
he would simply wander the building and use
their free informational services to learn

00:06:49.180 --> 00:06:51.180
more about medicine.

00:06:51.180 --> 00:06:56.289
Occasionally he would invent a work conference
that would supposedly take him to far-flung

00:06:56.289 --> 00:07:00.879
places in the world but he actually would
only travel to the airport and sleep in a

00:07:00.879 --> 00:07:02.840
motel close by.

00:07:02.840 --> 00:07:08.550
In the airport motel he would research new
medical technologies and various tourism information

00:07:08.550 --> 00:07:14.259
about whatever country he was supposedly visiting,
that way he would come home full of new information

00:07:14.259 --> 00:07:19.509
both medical and travel centered to keep up
the lies to his family.

00:07:19.509 --> 00:07:24.279
In order to keep up appearances and make ends
meet, he would take money from relatives and

00:07:24.279 --> 00:07:30.020
close acquaintances promising that he was
investing the money in hedge funds and international

00:07:30.020 --> 00:07:31.229
endeavors.

00:07:31.229 --> 00:07:36.230
His wife also worked full-time and during
this tenure of lies Romand took up with a

00:07:36.230 --> 00:07:42.490
wealthy mistress who loaned him 900,000 francs
(about 930,000 dollars).

00:07:42.490 --> 00:07:48.759
His lies had become unbearable and tenuous
however and instead of admitting that he was

00:07:48.759 --> 00:07:54.800
jobless and a fraud he decided to cover his
lies with actions far more sinister.

00:07:54.800 --> 00:08:01.939
On 9 January 1993 he took out 2000 francs
from his joint account with his wife and borrowed

00:08:01.939 --> 00:08:03.810
a gun from his father.

00:08:03.810 --> 00:08:09.749
He purchased a suppressor for that gun, a
.22 Long rifle carbine, and at the ammunition

00:08:09.749 --> 00:08:13.099
shop also purchased tear gas canisters.

00:08:13.099 --> 00:08:18.960
That evening he used a rolling pen to brutally
murder his wife, leaving her body in the bed

00:08:18.960 --> 00:08:20.330
all night.

00:08:20.330 --> 00:08:24.990
The next morning he woke his children , and
set them up with breakfast and cartoons as

00:08:24.990 --> 00:08:26.110
normal.

00:08:26.110 --> 00:08:30.509
Covering up their mothers absence with another
lie, he waited they were sleep until that

00:08:30.509 --> 00:08:34.440
night and used the gun to kill each as they
dreamt.

00:08:34.440 --> 00:08:39.800
His next victim would be his own parents where,
after having a meal with them he use the gun

00:08:39.800 --> 00:08:45.009
on both his mother and his father, as well
as their dog.

00:08:45.009 --> 00:08:50.350
His last victim was intended to be his well-off
ex-lover, someone had been having an affair

00:08:50.350 --> 00:08:52.319
with in the prior years.

00:08:52.319 --> 00:08:56.860
He picked her up under the guise of attending
a high-class dinner with one of his political

00:08:56.860 --> 00:09:02.889
connections, but instead he drove her to a
quiet road, and, pretending he was lost, asked

00:09:02.889 --> 00:09:06.089
her to get out to look for street signs.

00:09:06.089 --> 00:09:11.040
As she got out of the car he tried to strangle
her and then sprayed to tear gas at her face.

00:09:11.040 --> 00:09:17.110
But she would not stop fighting back and eventually
he acquiesced and apologized, and after swearing

00:09:17.110 --> 00:09:20.329
her to secrecy he drove her back home.

00:09:20.329 --> 00:09:24.850
Romand then went back to his own residence
where the bodies of his wife and children

00:09:24.850 --> 00:09:26.459
still lay.

00:09:26.459 --> 00:09:32.150
After watching television he poured gasoline
all over the house and set it ablaze.

00:09:32.150 --> 00:09:37.500
He then took some expired sleeping pills which
police thought he had hoped would kill him,

00:09:37.500 --> 00:09:42.579
but were actually just a cover-up to explain
how he did not rescue his wife and children

00:09:42.579 --> 00:09:44.690
in the fire.

00:09:44.690 --> 00:09:50.120
As if he wanted to kill himself he had access
to far more potent and powerful drugs that

00:09:50.120 --> 00:09:51.670
were not expired .

00:09:51.670 --> 00:09:57.060
Initially his lack of cooperation with police
was attributed to him being traumatized at

00:09:57.060 --> 00:10:10.060
the loss of his family but soon a more sinister
motive surfaced.

00:10:10.060 --> 00:10:16.440
In 1996 Romand was sentenced to life in prison
with no possibility of parole, while in prison

00:10:16.440 --> 00:10:21.519
he was clinically diagnosed with narcissistic
personality disorder, which came as no surprise

00:10:21.519 --> 00:10:26.069
to anyone who had come in contact with him.

00:10:26.069 --> 00:10:28.310
